45, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"the expected heatwaves\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hidalgo's position on air conditioning has been questioned due to the expected rise in temperatures during the upcoming European summer following the unprecedented heat in 2023.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 400, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999902547967486, \"rank\": 9.745298261231201e-06, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"the expected rise\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"temperatures\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming European summer\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"the unprecedented heat\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the athlete's village for Paris 2024 is set to be distinctive, featuring a cooling system that utilizes groundwater and structures positioned to reduce direct sunlight exposure.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9998647682169507e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athlete's village\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"a cooling system\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"groundwater\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"structures\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"direct sunlight exposure\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 763}]}, {\"sentenc