/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9993435212226525, \"rank\": 0.0006527068104345286, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 1740, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9993435212226525, \"rank\": 0.0006527068104345286, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"portable air conditioners\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"heat forecast\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"a rationale\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"their investment\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning units\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our clear wish is that there should be air-conditioning in all rooms,\\\" the Norwegian Committee told Reuters, with Brazil saying \\\"the heat forecast\\\" made it \\\"necessary to invest in renting air-conditioning units for the entire delegation\\\".\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.8524299464808924, \"rank\": 0.17311387724483432, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999906185622, \"rank\": 9.381328327922038e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbp