dia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.176154855470593e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"visits\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"the clever cooling system\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"floor\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"ceiling\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate zone\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"their federations\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"additional air conditioning\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The long-term vision for the athletes' village, which post-Games will become a neighborhood home to thousands of Parisians, has not been lost on Hidalgo.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2613, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999902547967486, \"rank\": 9.745298261231201e-06, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The long-term vision\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"a neighborhood\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These new buildings will not need air conditioning, so we are working for the long term,\\\" she stated, underscoring the sustainability of the project beyond the immediacy of the Olympics.\", \